# Controls and Compliance Checklist  
**Project:** Internal IT Security Audit – Botium Toys  
**Frameworks:** NIST CSF, PCI DSS, GDPR, SOC 1 & SOC 2  

---

### Controls Assessment

| Control | In Place? |
|---------|-----------|
| Least Privilege | No |
| Disaster Recovery Plans | No |
| Password Policies | Yes |
| Separation of Duties | No |
| Firewall | Yes |
| IDS | No |
| Backups | No |
| Antivirus Software | Yes |
| Legacy System Monitoring | Yes (manual, unscheduled) |
| Encryption | No |
| Password Mgmt System | No |
| Physical Locks | Yes |
| CCTV Surveillance | Yes |
| Fire Detection/Prevention | Yes |


---

## Compliance Assessment Checklist

### Payment Card Industry Data Security Standard (PCI DSS)

| Best Practice | Compliant |
|--------------|-----------|
| Only authorized users can access cardholder data | ❌ No |
| Credit card data is securely stored, processed, and transmitted | ❌ No |
| Encryption is implemented for cardholder data | ❌ No |
| Secure password management policies are enforced | ❌ No |

---

### General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR)

| Best Practice | Compliant |
|--------------|-----------|
| E.U. customer data is kept private and secure | ❌ No |
| Breach notification within 72 hours | ✅ Yes |
| Data is properly classified and inventoried | ❌ No |
| Privacy policies and procedures are enforced | ✅ Yes |

---

### System and Organization Controls (SOC 1 & SOC 2)

| Best Practice | Compliant |
|--------------|-----------|
| User access policies are established | ❌ No |
| Sensitive data (PII/SPII) is confidential | ❌ No |
| Data integrity is maintained | ✅ Yes |
| Data availability is ensured for authorized users | ✅ Yes |
